author: Letters to the editor
title: Jeb Bush, black Americans and 'free stuff': Letters to the Editor
text:
Jeb Bush and 'free stuff': I see Republican presidential candidate Jeb Bush is reaching out to African Americans by asking them to stop voting Democratic for all that "free stuff" the political party is said to hand out. Confused, I consulted my trusty, dog-eared copy of "The GOP Dictionary" and it appears Jeb meant jobless benefits, Social Security, Medicare and food stamps. You know, "free stuff" like that.
Sid Leader
Southeast Portland
